// Search Results
// Full-text search results page for onboarding topics.
// Query comes from the 'q' URL search parameter; results show topic, file type, and a highlighted snippet.

FUNCTION SearchResults()                                                EXPORT
  CALLS: search (onboarding-api)
  Read project from OnboardingContext. Read query 'q' from URL search params.
  When q or project changes: fetch results via onboardingApi.search.
  Render a list of result cards, each linking to /onboarding/topic/:topicName.
  Each card shows the topic name, file type label, and a snippet with highlighted match terms (rendered as raw HTML).
  Show "No results found" when the search returns nothing.
